        <p class="h4">In this section</p>
        <ul>
                              <li><p><a href="https://www.bfi.org.uk/bfi-film-academy-opportunities-young-creatives" class="">BFI Film Academy: opportunities for young creatives</a></p></li>
                    <li><p><a href="https://www.bfi.org.uk/get-funding-support/progress-my-creative-career-grow-my-business" class="">Get funding to progress my creative career</a></p></li>
                    <li><p><a href="https://www.bfi.org.uk/find-resources-events-teachers" class="">Find resources and events for teachers</a></p></li>
